				"description": "<p>When you activate your rage, you can let out a devastating roar, strike the ground or something similar. Creatures within 10 feet of you must make a Constitution save against your maneuver DC or take 4d4 points of thunder damage and be deafened for one minute. A creature that succeeds on its save takes half damage and is not deafened. A creature deafened this way can repeat the save at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on a success.</p>",
